  "description": "<p>🏆 Dynamic Famous Branding Sales Leader🏆</p><p><br /></p><p>⚜️Entry level are all welcome⚜️</p><p><br /></p><p>🚀 Where your drive fuels your success! 🌟</p><p>📍 Office located @ Raffles / Boat Quay📈 Career progression opportunities</p><p>🥊 Training provided</p><p><br /></p><p>Looking out for:</p><p>- Fresh grad/ORD & Career switch</p><p>- Leadership & guidance 📚</p><p>- Flexible schedule 📆</p><p>- Personal development 🧑‍🎓</p><p>⁃ Work well independently and in team environment 🤜🏽🤛🏽</p><p>- Overseas training & trips ✈️</p><p>(Melbourne, Malaysia, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Indonesia)</p><p>Responsibilities for this role:</p><p><br /></p><p>⁃ Conduct face-to-face sales presentation 📊</p><p>⁃ Provide great customer service 🔊</p><p>⁃ Able to adapt rapid changes 💱</p><p><br /></p><p>Singaporean and PR only.</p><p><br /></p><p>Do not hesitate to APPLY! Dropped your resume in WhatsApp 81714219 @Mak</p>",
